{"tid":1074501,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"集氣 貓貓生病記","createTime":"2019-03-23T12:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T07:59:46.000Z","uid":181750,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0f0446597a870ff526c9e6edb337d1d5f3c02e","tid":1074501,"uid":181750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:20:59.000Z","msg":"長文<br />\n<br />\n貓貓係7歲半大既英短<br />\n平時乾糧濕糧都食 零食反而唔多好 又中意飲水<br />\n所以由細到大都都冇咩大病痛<br />\n<br />\n點知琴日凌晨左右 <br />\n男友發現貓貓行路擺下擺下 好似飲醉酒wing左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今日訓醒情況都係冇改善<br />\n佢行行下路會無啦啦企唔穩 向左/右一邊撻底<br />\n但都仲好精神 又肯食野飲水 <br />\n<br />\n下午去左土瓜灣一間獸醫診所check下咩事<br />\n個女獸醫好細心 <br />\n檢查左好耐<br />\n佢話 好明顯貓貓半邊面部神經都冇左感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右眼唔識得眨眼 可能係個腦有事 （因為耳仔好乾淨最近又冇搞過耳仔又冇剝過牙）<br />\n因而連帶佢半邊身手腳同平衡感都有影響<br />\n要refer我地去太平道睇神經專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太平道個邊睇左貓貓病歷之後 <br />\n就話聽日有期 睇郭醫生<br />\n我上網goggle過呂醫生係最好  但話冇哂位唔俾期我都冇計<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲睇過佢？<br />\n同埋有冇遇過貓貓有咁既情況？<br />\n我有上網睇過有貓主話呢d可能係神經系統問題 <br />\n食返d維生素B-1就冇事 <br />\n但呢刻我唔敢亂咁俾野佢食<br />\n<br />\n依家佢好似都唔知自己出左事咁 <br />\n返到屋企又四圍行 擺下擺下 又要跳上張枱唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢早日康復<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41500f4767db86d3c0580cc6378a7eaa729e098","tid":1074501,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n希望快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屋企5隻貓幫你集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31bb5d8e270d826e2d88ff48fc804292ed02fe8","tid":1074501,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"未遇過咁樣，唯有幫樓主推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b36d302c77ea09c8e1a34bbb1b10bcc4b2c90","tid":1074501,"uid":144815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"祝貓貓早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bbd27f28d569c26c058bf33d0964adbc59d1d8","tid":1074501,"uid":200580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"貓貓要快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f00b1bd95667b93702e6bcb45f4c13a22e22a1","tid":1074501,"uid":98167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"幫推 貓貓要快啲好返啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e208acc8fab350c06e1023a8eae4e611bc103de","tid":1074501,"uid":181750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"好在佢成晚都好好胃口 <br />\n係咁食<br />\n<br />\n不過訓覺時右眼都係合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去貓砂盆屙完尿 刮刮下砂 <br />\n我又聽到bang一聲 <br />\n就知道佢又企唔穩仆親了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f168a3a08264a9c33bd3e3d2a215b8c277f6e52","tid":1074501,"uid":3002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"唔好諗咁多，估估下個人仲亂，盡快盡快睇醫生先再諗一步，今晚陪住佢抱佢訓<br />\n<br />\n我隻以前都有睇太平道，希望佢地都醫好你貓，加油"},{"pid":"1ad11195576399881b6cc30def21093a012ba36f","tid":1074501,"uid":101522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"幫巴打集氣 記得返黎update下情況我地知"},{"pid":"262f480ccc388434e1ac8e16cf5a2016a2f8dc94","tid":1074501,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"貓貓要快d 好番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40812d0b4754228c7aa0c023fb7e767e4e1e1ed7","tid":1074501,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"希望貓貓無事快啲好番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe631610a4bdb7704246cb20cafbcd272a23ba07","tid":1074501,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad6c63448571e0440aff9b4cefdac1b33431b6c","tid":1074501,"uid":181750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"睇完了<br />\n<br />\n醫生幾肯定貓貓係半邊面癱左<br />\n再加上平衡感出現問題<br />\n因為連接住面部同平衡既神經線係由大腦經耳仔出黎<br />\n有可能係中耳炎影響到神經接收<br />\n又有可能係個腦出事<br />\n<br />\n之後驗埋血<br />\n除左GLOB球蛋白同膽固醇高左d之外<br />\n其他指標都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n醫生話膽固醇高同今次病發冇太大關係<br />\n唯一令人擔心既就係球蛋白超標 (正常2.8-5.1; 佢5.4)<br />\n反映到貓貓體內係有炎症 <br />\n但咩部位就要照MRI先知道<br />\n<br />\n我地冇同佢照到MRI<br />\n一黎要全身麻醉<br />\n二黎好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成萬幾蚊<br />\n所以醫生開左2星期抗生素俾貓貓食 <br />\n觀察住有冇好轉到<br />\n<br />\n萬一情況差左<br />\n都做定打算最後係要照MRI<br />\n<br />\n如果照完一切正常 <br />\n就大機會係貓貓自身既神經系統跳左制<br />\n呢方面冇得醫 唯有靠佢自己康復<br />\n<br />\n但照到出黎係有腫瘤/腦膜炎既 <br />\n就要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心驚佢會捱唔住<br />\n<br />\n依家除左準時喂佢食藥之外<br />\n都冇咩可以做到<br />\n希望佢自己都努力打贏呢場仗啦！"},{"pid":"58fe89c38851bfccf45a0d87beb103108d4b8bc9","tid":1074501,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"異短半歲大時試過同樣情況，行路擺擺下半邊臉郁唔到，將手放到好近都唔識眨眼，望住佢眨唔到眼成眼都係眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生都係開維他命b<br />\n嗰陣佢仲要成日打乞痴，日日一大堆鼻涕噴出嚟，唔知會唔會係感冒菌上埋腦<br />\n後來過咗兩星期好返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0787bcb09716080827eb07382772f3d35976e34","tid":1074501,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:54:37.000Z","msg":"醫生話最緊要係佢肯食，胃口好嘅話情況都唔會太差"},{"pid":"832f4129b664513bf1f5a0c077224ed7a700bf25","tid":1074501,"uid":217214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T20:47:02.000Z","msg":"加油啊 希望佢快啲好番啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339b78dd7adf9b6eeeedf2117bc2a01a4300fcff","tid":1074501,"uid":181750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fe89c38851bfccf45a0d87beb103108d4b8bc9","tid":1074501,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"異短半歲大時試過同樣情況，行路擺擺下半邊臉郁唔到，將手放到好近都唔識眨眼，望住佢眨唔到眼成眼都係眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生都係開維他命b<br />\n嗰陣佢仲要成日打乞痴，日日一大堆鼻涕噴出嚟，唔知會唔會係感冒菌上埋腦<br />\n後來過咗兩星期好返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"!!!!!!!係呀 <br />\n<br />\n呢排我都見佢有打乞痴多左<br />\n<br />\n我自己都有買維他命b俾佢食 <br />\n加埋d抗生素 <br />\n希望好得返啦<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打你呀 <br />\n好似見到一絲希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都多謝其他巴絲既鼓勵！<br />\n會定期再update大家"},{"pid":"b6cf420558d57925cfe925393cf59068dbec09c7","tid":1074501,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"中風"},{"pid":"8375e7d0447386b82194635146fb76b41c6a4287","tid":1074501,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339b78dd7adf9b6eeeedf2117bc2a01a4300fcff","tid":1074501,"uid":181750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fe89c38851bfccf45a0d87beb103108d4b8bc9","tid":1074501,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"異短半歲大時試過同樣情況，行路擺擺下半邊臉郁唔到，將手放到好近都唔識眨眼，望住佢眨唔到眼成眼都係眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生都係開維他命b<br />\n嗰陣佢仲要成日打乞痴，日日一大堆鼻涕噴出嚟，唔知會唔會係感冒菌上埋腦<br />\n後來過咗兩星期好返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"!!!!!!!係呀 <br />\n<br />\n呢排我都見佢有打乞痴多左<br />\n<br />\n我自己都有買維他命b俾佢食 <br />\n加埋d抗生素 <br />\n希望好得返啦<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打你呀 <br />\n好似見到一絲希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都多謝其他巴絲既鼓勵！<br />\n會定期再update大家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:27:44.000Z","msg":"嗰陣我仲記得十號風球帶唔到佢睇獸醫，好無助。第二朝一落波即刻帶佢去睇，好好彩佢冇事，希望你隻貓都係一樣情況好快好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw打乞痴多唔多鼻涕？如果多鼻涕又持續一般長時間可能要醫生開其他藥，我隻貓半年睇咗三個獸醫先睇到一個開啱藥斷到尾"},{"pid":"1557ecd3e51309912404524f1e20ab203b4feeff","tid":1074501,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"加油"}]}